* {{ill|Nikko Toshogu|ja|日光東照宮}}
* {{ill|Kamigamo Shrine|ja|上賀茂神社}}
* {{ill|Iwashimizu Hachimangu|ja|石清水八幡宮}}
* {{ill|Yoshikawa Hachiman Shrine (Toyono)|ja|吉川八幡神社 (豊能町)}}
* {{ill|Soma Nakamura Shrine|ja|相馬中村神社}}
* {{ill|Kotohira-gu|ja|金刀比羅宮}}
* {{ill|Komuro Sengen Shrine|ja|冨士山下宮小室浅間神社}}
* {{ill|Ishikiri Tsurugiya Shrine|ja|石切剣箭神社}}
* {{ill|Kashima Katori Hongu (Yamato Province)|ja|大和国 鹿島香取本宮}}
* {{ill|Niukawakami Shrine Shimosha|ja|丹生川上神社下社}}
* {{ill|Oishi Shrine (Kyoto Yamashina)|ja|大石神社 (京都市山科区)}}

== Song Related to Shinme ==
* From the "Azuma Kagami," Kenkyū 6 (1195), April 27, Kajiwara Kagetoki dedicated a Shinme at Sumiyoshi Shrine with this poem:
** 「我が君の 手向の駒を 引きつれて 行末遠き しるしあらわせ」

